From git@z Thu Jan  1 00:00:00 1970
Subject: [PATCH 21/30] x86/bugs: Don't fill RSB on context switch with
 eIBRS
From: Josh Poimboeuf <jpoimboe@kernel.org>
Date: Mon, 14 Apr 2025 09:28:38 -0400
